  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK743">
<l>uyarvakalan tiṇmai yarumaiyin nāṉki</l>
<l>ṉamaivaraṇā meṉṟuraikku nūl</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The learned say that a fortress is an enclosure having these four (qualities) viz., height, breadth, strength and inaccessibility.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
